        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Remove the freezer bowl from the freezer and take it to the Cusin Art  icecream
                    machine</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Place the freezer bowl in the base of the ice cream machine. </cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Place the arm in the freezer bowl taking note that it will not fit tightly. It
