            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Place the lid over the base making sure that it is oreiented to the right of
                    the center. Turn clockwise to lock. </cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>The machine has three different functions: Ice Cream, Sorbet, and Gelato.
                    Select Ice Cream and a beep will be heard </cmd>
